Karansul's trouble
Karansul has problems. He no longer receives any news from the area where his factories are located. You must find out why and solve the problem.
#subobj  1
Reaching one of the bridges
To reach Karansul's factories, cross one of the bridges at the eastern part of the lake - the northern or the southern one.
#subobj  2
Eliminating "trouble"
To complete this quest you must kill all the Trolls, Tigers and elementals near the factories and the bridges.